{"tid":2074410,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"最近返KT","createTime":"2020-06-22T05:39:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T05:06:33.000Z","uid":50483,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c1108382689ff8b2232d37297b0163614149d0dc","tid":2074410,"uid":50483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T05:39:34.000Z","msg":"近排返觀塘碼頭附近發現冇乜野好食<br />\n大部份既餐廳都偏貴<br />\n於是打開和你eat睇下附近有咩黃店<br />\n發現觀塘碼頭熟食中心一樓有間新海濱茶餐廳<br />\n價錢都係33-40$左右包野飲<br />\n算牙份量又夠大<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iRBJBYj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiRBJBYj.jpg&h=f3c9b24c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tVfRLRN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtVfRLRN.jpg&h=0c9a9326&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6kTv1qc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6kTv1qc.jpg&h=f8f7be2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n的確係糧尾最好既選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果口渴 又可以去宏利金融中心支持Nuttea<br />\n<br />\n支持黃色經濟圈 你我有責<br />\n（本人只推薦食得落至好食既黃店<br />\n難食既黃店 本人必踩）<br />\n覺得唔啱隨便屌我 <br />\n<br />\n請立即下載和你eat 支持黃色經濟圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ec8a11f5f613cb3552ef3a96fdfdcf841ddd947","tid":2074410,"uid":33359,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T05:44:03.000Z","msg":"佢樓上間拿督都好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過好似唔是黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3737421bd6bee2de3986cfde3fea2e0922417341","tid":2074410,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T05:45:27.000Z","msg":"nutta得個奶蓋好少少<br />\nbtw記得去食船麵, 就快執<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f921a0eebe6ddec6df3f0d904808bbc7494e2d40","tid":2074410,"uid":50483,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T05:52:15.000Z","msg":"唔該黃店之間自己做返啲比較<br />\n我唔指名邊啲餐廳<br />\n但有我食過最差既黃店<br />\n白烚肥牛倒啲日清咖哩落去<br />\n飯又硬 賣$33UP<br />\n叫個麵 又冇味 個湯又唔熱<br />\n唔好以為你係黃店唔驚無客<br />\n黃店之間係應該存在競爭<br />\n好食就係好食<br />\n難食就係難食<br />\n難食唔會因為你係黃而我夾硬講好食"},{"pid":"0a276673d166ba9e628e0391bce0197333b66dcb","tid":2074410,"uid":50483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T05:54:16.000Z","msg":"本人要特別讚一讚黃店 慈雲山八道餐廳<br />\n啲野食由唔好食 去到依家我每日都想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b4de595a078123549a462bc4fbd2f6096902430","tid":2074410,"uid":36471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T05:54:59.000Z","msg":"Pusg"},{"pid":"1d620e18776ad8c3921f98a2f72ba05fc6eb2fda","tid":2074410,"uid":50483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7ec8a11f5f613cb3552ef3a96fdfdcf841ddd947","tid":2074410,"uid":33359,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T05:44:03.000Z","msg":"佢樓上間拿督都好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過好似唔是黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T05:56:02.000Z","msg":"佢無表態 我見好多人讚 但我會首選黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b235b1795b7b11ccfaf6ed59f5605f51d6c57286","tid":2074410,"uid":50483,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T06:00:34.000Z","msg":"仲有間果汁店係宏利<br />\n叫cling 唔記得 都係推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a237ac3bf76a4f4ba3450b3f6290c20d77fc656","tid":2074410,"uid":211878,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T06:05:11.000Z","msg":"Ching應該同我好撚近<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行遠少少駱駝柒都有啲唔錯嘅黃店 首推Cool Cousins"},{"pid":"695be59698aa6750706c707e8f916b33ae6c7407","tid":2074410,"uid":50483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"p